      <title>leetcode | 342. 4的幂 | 位运算的巧妙应用</title>
      <link href="2021/05/31/%E4%BD%8D%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A7%E5%A6%99%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/"/>
      <url>2021/05/31/%E4%BD%8D%E8%BF%90%E7%AE%97%E7%9A%84%E5%B7%A7%E5%A6%99%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="题目"><a href="#题目" class="headerlink" title="题目"></a>题目</h2><p>给定一个整数，写一个函数来判断它是否是 4 的幂次方。如果是，返回 true ；否则，返回 false 。</p><p>整数 n 是 4 的幂次方需满足：存在整数 x 使得 n == $4^x$</p><h2 id="思路"><a href="#思路" class="headerlink" title="思路"></a>思路</h2><p>经观察，不难发现：</p><ol><li>4的幂次方一定是2的幂次方</li><li>写成二进制后，可知4的幂的二进制表示中只会出现一位1，而且该1一定出现在奇数位上</li><li>在n为2的幂次方的前提下，若n除以3的余数为1，则为4的幂次方，否则不然</li></ol><p>至此，便得出了解决问题所需要的所有条件。下文选取了思路中的1和3用以解决问题，代码如下：</p><h2 id="代码"><a href="#代码" class="headerlink" title="代码"></a>代码</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Solution</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="function"><span class="keyword">bool</span> <span class="title">isPowerOfFour</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 1. n&amp;(n-1)用于判断n是否2的幂次方</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (n &lt; <span class="number">0</span> || n&amp;(n<span class="number">-1</span>)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment">// 2. 在1.的前提下，判断余数</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> n % <span class="number">3</span> == <span class="number">1</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="附录1：用余数判断一个2的幂次方是否是4的幂次方"><a href="#附录1：用余数判断一个2的幂次方是否是4的幂次方" class="headerlink" title="附录1：用余数判断一个2的幂次方是否是4的幂次方"></a>附录1：用余数判断一个2的幂次方是否是4的幂次方</h2><p>取$k\in N$，则在2的幂次方中，4的幂次方一定满足：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{align*}2^{2k} &= 4^x\\ &= (3+1)^x\\ &= C(x,0) \times 3^0 \times 1^x +  \underbrace {\sum ^{x} _{i=1} C(x,i) \times 3^i \times 1^{ (x-i)}}_{x-1个\space3的幂次方之和}\\&=1+各个3的幂次方之和\end{align*}</script><p>而2的幂次方中，不是4的幂次方又满足：</p><script type="math/tex; mode=display">\begin{align*}2^{2k+1}&=4^x\times2 \\ &=(3+1)^x \times(3-1)\\&=(1+各个3的幂次方)\times(3-1)\\&=2+各个3的幂次方之和\times2\end{align*}</script><p>观察可知，在n为2的幂次方的前提下，若n除以3的余数为1，则为4的幂次方，否则不然。</p><h2 id="附录2：有意思的二进制数"><a href="#附录2：有意思的二进制数" class="headerlink" title="附录2：有意思的二进制数"></a>附录2：有意思的二进制数</h2><p>0xaaaaaaaa = 10101010101010101010101010101010 (偶数位为1，奇数位为0）</p><p>0x55555555 = 1010101010101010101010101010101 (偶数位为0，奇数位为1）</p><p>0x33333333 = 110011001100110011001100110011 (1和0每隔两位交替出现)</p><p>0xcccccccc = 11001100110011001100110011001100 (0和1每隔两位交替出现)</p><p>0x0f0f0f0f = 00001111000011110000111100001111 (1和0每隔四位交替出现)</p><p>0xf0f0f0f0 = 11110000111100001111000011110000 (0和1每隔四位交替出现)</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
